Avocet Mining Rises in London After Reporting Guinea Results

-- B y   A m a n d a   J o r d a n
-- 
2011-03-16T16:45:25Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-03-16/avocet-mining-rises-in-london-after-reporting-guinea-results-1-.html
  Avocet Mining Plc (AVM) , which today
announced results of drilling at Koulekoun,  Guinea , rose 0.7
percent to 213.25 pence at the 4:30 p.m. close in  London . The
shares earlier jumped as much as 7.8 percent, the biggest gain
in two weeks.  To contact the reporter on this story:
